data.eml:eml: Descriptions of Neboissomina, new genus and 6 new species of Ecnomidae from Australia (Trichoptera)

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Cartwright, David I. (2011): Descriptions of Neboissomina, new genus and 6 new species of Ecnomidae from Australia (Trichoptera). Zootaxa 2736: 17-30, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.202023
